WEBVTT

00:10.777 --> 00:13.279
You're traveling
through another dimension-

00:13.314 --> 00:16.399
a dimension not only of sight
and sound, but of mind,

00:16.434 --> 00:18.284
a journey into a wondrous land

00:18.319 --> 00:20.153
whose boundaries
are that of imagination.

00:20.188 --> 00:23.907
Your next stop,
the twilight zone.

